config CHARGER_EXTCON_MAX77660
	tristate "MAX77660 battery charger and external connection support"
	depends on MFD_MAX77660 && EXTCON && REGULATOR
	select BATTERY_CHARGER_GAUGE_COMM
	help
	 MAX77660 is a pmic for smartphones and tablets which supports
	 battery charging feature. It also detect the presence of HOST
	 cable. Implement the notification mechanism for Host cable connection
	 through extcon framework.
	 Say Y here to enable battery charging driver support for
	 maxim MAX77660 chipset.

